

Add words to access addresses outside the constrained space.
X   ALLOCATE    allocate and zero a chunk of memory
X   MDUMP       Dispay memory at address.
X   FREE        Release memory
X   GET         Read machine natural word size (e.g. 32 bit) from address
X   CGET        Read a byte.
    WGET        Read 16 bits
X   SET         Write word to address.
X   CSET        Write byte.
    WSET        Write 16 bits.

    FILL        Write byte to area of memeory
    ERASE       Zero area of memory

X   CMOVE       Copy memory, one byte at a time.
    MOVE        Copy 32 bit words.
                Copy bytes from arena to memory.
                Copy bytes to arena from memory.

